title: GachaCCClient
content:
print("Running GACHA CC!!")
local db={}
local DATABASE="https://drive.hellholestudios.top/gachaCC/"

function drawRemoteNFP(paste_id)
    shell.run("delete image.nfp") --delete file if it already exists
    shell.run("pastebin", "get", paste_id, "image.nfp") --fetch NFP image from pastebin at given paste_id
    local image = paintutils.loadImage("image.nfp") 
    paintutils.drawImage(image, 0, 0)
end

function gacha2(star)
    local name={}
    local n=0
    for key,value in pairs(db) do
        if value['rarity']==star then
            name[n]=value
            n=n+1
        end
    end

    if n==0 then
        return "ZYQ"
    else
        return name[math.random(0,n-1)]
    end
end

function gacha()
    local rng=math.random()
    local res="ZYQ"
    if rng<=0.01 then --return 6
        res=gacha2(6)
    elseif rng<=0.08 then --return 5
        res=gacha2(5)
    elseif rng<=0.4 then
        res=gacha2(4)
    elseif rng<=0.9 then
        res=gacha2(3)
    else
        res=gacha2(2)
    end

    -- display image
    shell.run("delete image.nfp") --delete file if it already exists
    shell.run("wget", DATABASE.."source/"..res['name']..".nfp", "image.nfp") --fetch NFP image from pastebin at given paste_id
    local image = paintutils.loadImage("image.nfp") 
    paintutils.drawImage(image, 0, 0)

    -- print stuff
    local p=peripheral.find("printer")
    p.newPage()
    p.setPageTitle(res['name'].." Card!")
    p.setCursorPos(1,1)
    p.write(res['name'])
    p.setCursorPos(1,21)
    for i=1,res['rarity'] do
        p.write('*')
    end

    p.setCursorPos(13,1)
    p.write(''..res['value'][0])
    
    p.setCursorPos(25,11)
    p.write(''..res['value'][1])
    
    p.setCursorPos(13,21)
    p.write(''..res['value'][2])
    
    p.setCursorPos(1,11)
    p.write(''..res['value'][3])

    p.endPage()
    
    term.setCursorPos(1,30)
    term.setBackgroundColor(colors.black)
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.write("You got: "..res.."!! Press anywhere to continue!")
    os.pullEvent('monitor_touch')
end

-- check peripherals
local p=peripheral.find("printer")
local m=peripheral.find("monitor")
local s=peripheral.find("speaker")

if p==nil or m==nil or s==nil then
    printError("Need a printer, monitor and speaker!")
    return
end

term.redirect(m)
term.setCursorPos(1,1)
term.setBackgroundColor(colors.black)
term.setTextColor(colors.white)
term.clear()
if term.isColor() then
else
    printError("Monitor is not advanced!")
    return
end

while true do
    -- show logo
    drawRemoteNFP("ykMw7kYz")
    term.setCursorPos(1,30)
    term.setBackgroundColor(colors.black)
    term.setTextColor(colors.white)
    term.write("Welcome to GachaCC!! Press anywhere to 10 roll!!")

    os.pullEvent("monitor_touch")

    -- download database
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1,30)
    print("Downloading database...")
    local req=http.get(DATABASE.."data/list.json")
    local txt=req.readAll()
    db=textutils.unserializeJSON(txt)
    req.close()

    -- real gacha
    for i=1,10 do
        gacha()
    end
end

title: CC: Tweaked - CLI To-Do
content:
local todoList = {}

while true do
    print("Welcome to your To-do list!")
    print("1: View To-do list")
    print("2: Add item to To-do list")
    print("3: Delete item from To-do list")
    print("4: Edit item from To-do list")
    print("5: Exit program")
    print("Enter your choice:")

    local choice = tonumber(read())

    if choice == 1 then
        print("Your To-do list:")
        for i, item in ipairs(todoList) do
            print(i .. ": " .. item)
        end
    elseif choice == 2 then
        print("Enter the item to add:")
        local item = read()
        table.insert(todoList, item)
    elseif choice == 3 then
        print("Enter the number of the item to delete:")
        for i, item in ipairs(todoList) do
            print(i .. ": " .. item)
        end
        local itemNumber = tonumber(read())
        table.remove(todoList, itemNumber)
    elseif choice == 4 then
        print("Enter the number of the item to edit:")
        for i, item in ipairs(todoList) do
            print(i .. ": " .. item)
        end
        local itemNumber = tonumber(read())
        print("Enter the new text for the item:")
        local newText = read()
        todoList[itemNumber] = newText
    elseif choice == 5 then
        break
    else
        print("Invalid choice! Please enter a number between 1 and 5.")
    end

    print("\n")
end

title: udp-traffic.ps1
content:
function Send-UdpDatagram
{
      Param ([string] $EndPoint, 
      [int] $Port, 
      [string] $Message)

      $IP = [System.Net.Dns]::GetHostAddresses($EndPoint) 
      $Address = [System.Net.IPAddress]::Parse($IP) 
      $EndPoints = New-Object System.Net.IPEndPoint($Address, $Port) 
      $Socket = New-Object System.Net.Sockets.UDPClient 
      $EncodedText = [Text.Encoding]::ASCII.GetBytes($Message) 
      $SendMessage = $Socket.Send($EncodedText, $EncodedText.Length, $EndPoints) 
      $Socket.Close() 
} 

Send-UdpDatagram -EndPoint "<REMOTE_GW_IP>" -Port 4500 -Message "test.mymetric:0|c"
Send-UdpDatagram -EndPoint "<REMOTE_GW_IP>" -Port 500 -Message "test.myothermetric:0|c"

def startTend

    for i in 0...6
        specie=Tent::MONS[rand(Tent::MONS.length)]
        numspecie=getID(PBSpecies,specie)
        print specie if numspecie==0
        poke=PokeBattle_Pokemon.new(specie,30)
        poke.setItem(Tent::ITEMS[rand(Tent::ITEMS.length)])
        team.push(poke)
        list.push(poke.name)
    end
    pbFacilityTeam(false)
    for i in 0...3
      numpoke=Kernel.pbMessage("¿Escoge #{3-i} pokémon?",list)
      pbAddPokemonSilent(team[numpoke])
      list[numpoke]=nil
      list.compact!
      team[numpoke]=nil
      team.compact!
    end
end

def pbFacilityTeam(recover=false,change=nil)
    if recover; $Trainer.party=$game_variables[PTVAR] ; $game_variables[PTVAR]=nil
    else ; $game_variables[PTVAR]=$Trainer.party ; $Trainer.party=[] ; end ; end

def chosseTrainerType
    trtype=Tent::TRTYPES[rand(Tent::TRTYPES.length)]
    $game_variables[TRVAR]=getID(PBTrainers,trtype) if trtype.is_a?(Symbol)
end


def startTentTrainer
    party=[]
    for i in 0...3
        specie=Tent::MONS[rand(Tent::MONS.length)]
        numspecie=getID(PBSpecies,specie)
        print specie if numspecie==0
        poke=PokeBattle_Pokemon.new(specie,30)
        poke.setItem(Tent::ITEMS[rand(Tent::ITEMS.length)])
        party[i]=poke
    end
    #party[1].tera_ace=true if $PokemonBag.pbHasItem?(:TERAORB)
    $game_variables[TMVAR]=party
    trtype=$game_variables[TRVAR]
    customTrainerBattle(createTrainer(trtype,"¿¿??",party),"",false,true)
end

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Written by Stochastic, except for customTrainerBattle method which is a
# modified version of pbTrainerBattle method.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

BR_DRAW = 5
BR_LOSS = 2
BR_WIN = 1

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# species - Name of the species, e.g. "PIKACHU"
# level - Level
# moveset - Optional. Array of moves, e.g. [:MUDSLAP, :THUNDERBOLT, :VINEWHIP]
# If not specified, pokemon will be created with moves learned by leveling.
# The pokemon doesn't need to be able to learn the given moves, they can be
# arbitary.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
def createPokemon(species, level, moveset=nil)
  begin
    poke = PokeBattle_Pokemon.new(species, level)
    poke.moves = convertMoves(moveset) if moveset
    poke.shinyflag = false
    return poke
  rescue
    return PokeBattle_Pokemon.new("PIKACHU", 5)
  end
end

def convertMoves(moves)
  moves.map! {|m| PBMove.new(getMoveID(m))}
  return moves
end

# provide move like this; :TACKLE
def getMoveID(move)
  return getConst(PBMoves,move)
end

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Creates a trainer with specified id, name, party, and optionally, items.
# Does not depend on defined trainers, only on trainer types
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
def createTrainer(trainerid,trainername,party,items=[])
  
  name = pbGetMessageFromHash(MessageTypes::TrainerNames, trainername)
  opponent = PokeBattle_Trainer.new(name, trainerid)
  opponent.setForeignID($Trainer) if $Trainer
  for i in party
    i.trainerID=opponent.id
    i.ot="DESCONOCIDO"
    i.otgender=opponent.gender
  end
  opponent.party = party
  
  return [opponent,items,party]
end

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Initiates trainer battle. This is a modified pbTrainerBattle method.
#
# trainer - custom PokeBattle_Trainer provided by the user
# endspeech - what the trainer says in-battle when defeated
# doublebattle - Optional. Set it to true if you want a double battle
# canlose - Optional. Set it to true if you want your party to be healed after battle,
#and if you don't want to be sent to a pokemon center if you lose
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
def customTrainerBattle(trainer,endspeech,doublebattle=false,canlose=false)
  trainerparty=0 # added by SH
  if $Trainer.pokemonCount==0
    Kernel.pbMessage(_INTL("SKIPPING BATTLE...")) if $DEBUG
    return BR_LOSS # changed by SH
  end
  if !$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer && $Trainer.ablePokemonCount>1 &&
     pbMapInterpreterRunning?
    thisEvent=pbMapInterpreter.get_character(0)
    triggeredEvents=$game_player.pbTriggeredTrainerEvents([2],false)
    otherEvent=[]
    for i in triggeredEvents
      if i.id!=thisEvent.id && !$game_self_switches[[$game_map.map_id,i.id,"A"]]
        otherEvent.push(i)
      end
    end
    if otherEvent.length==1
      if trainer[2].length<=3
        $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer=[trainer,thisEvent.id,endspeech,doublebattle]
        return BR_LOSS # changed by SH
      end
    end
  end
  
  if $PokemonGlobal.partner && ($PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer || doublebattle)
    othertrainer=PokeBattle_Trainer.new(
       $PokemonGlobal.partner[1],$PokemonGlobal.partner[0])
    othertrainer.id=$PokemonGlobal.partner[2]
    othertrainer.party=$PokemonGlobal.partner[3]
    playerparty=[]
    for i in 0...$Trainer.party.length
      playerparty[i]=$Trainer.party[i]
    end
    for i in 0...othertrainer.party.length
      playerparty[6+i]=othertrainer.party[i]
    end
    fullparty1=true
    playertrainer=[$Trainer,othertrainer]
    doublebattle=true
  else
    playerparty=$Trainer.party
    playertrainer=$Trainer
    fullparty1=false
  end
  if $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer
    combinedParty=[]
    fullparty2=false
    if false
      if $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2].length>3
        raise _INTL("Opponent 1's party has more than three Pokémon, which is not allowed")
      end
      if trainer[2].length>3
        raise _INTL("Opponent 2's party has more than three Pokémon, which is not allowed")
      end
    elsif $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2].length>3 || trainer[2].length>3
      for i in 0...$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2].length
        combinedParty[i]=$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2][i]
      end
      for i in 0...trainer[2].length
        combinedParty[6+i]=trainer[2][i]
      end
      fullparty2=true
    else
      for i in 0...$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2].length
        combinedParty[i]=$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][2][i]
      end
      for i in 0...trainer[2].length
        combinedParty[3+i]=trainer[2][i]
      end
      fullparty2=false
    end
    scene=pbNewBattleScene
    battle=PokeBattle_Battle.new(scene,playerparty,combinedParty,playertrainer,
       [$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][0],trainer[0]])
    trainerbgm=pbGetTrainerBattleBGM(
       [$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][0],trainer[0]])
    battle.fullparty1=fullparty1
    battle.fullparty2=fullparty2
    battle.doublebattle=battle.pbDoubleBattleAllowed?()
    battle.endspeech=$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[2]
    battle.endspeech2=endspeech
    battle.items=[$PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[0][1],trainer[1]]
  else
    scene=pbNewBattleScene
    battle=PokeBattle_Battle.new(scene,playerparty,trainer[2],playertrainer,trainer[0])
    battle.fullparty1=fullparty1
    battle.doublebattle=doublebattle ? battle.pbDoubleBattleAllowed?() : false
    battle.endspeech=endspeech
    battle.items=trainer[1]
    trainerbgm=pbStringToAudioFile(TENTBGM)
  end
  if Input.press?(Input::CTRL) && $DEBUG
    Kernel.pbMessage(_INTL("SKIPPING BATTLE..."))
    Kernel.pbMessage(_INTL("AFTER LOSING..."))
    Kernel.pbMessage(battle.endspeech)
    Kernel.pbMessage(battle.endspeech2) if battle.endspeech2
    if $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer
      pbMapInterpreter.pbSetSelfSwitch(
         $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[1],"A",true
      )
      $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer=nil
    end
    return BR_WIN # changed by SH
  end
  Events.onStartBattle.trigger(nil,nil)
  battle.internalbattle=false
  pbPrepareBattle(battle)
  restorebgm=true
  decision=0
  pbBattleAnimation(trainerbgm,trainer[0].trainertype,trainer[0].name) { 
     pbSceneStandby {
        decision=battle.pbStartBattle(canlose)
     }
     if $PokemonGlobal.partner
       pbHealAll
       for i in $PokemonGlobal.partner[3]; i.heal; end
     end
     if decision==2 || decision==5
       if canlose
         for i in $Trainer.party; i.heal; end
         for i in 0...10
           Graphics.update
         end
       else
         $game_system.bgm_unpause
         $game_system.bgs_unpause
         Kernel.pbStartOver
       end
     else
       Events.onEndBattle.trigger(nil,decision)
       if decision==1
         if $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer
           pbMapInterpreter.pbSetSelfSwitch(
              $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer[1],"A",true
           )
         end
       end
     end
  }
  Input.update
  $PokemonTemp.waitingTrainer=nil
  list=[]
  for i in $game_variables[TMVAR]
    list.push(i.name)
  end
  for i in $Trainer.party
    i.heal
  end
  return decision if !pbConfirmMessage("¿Quieres algún Pokémon del rival?")
  numpoke=Kernel.pbMessage("¿Qué Pokémon quieres?",list)
  poke=$game_variables[TMVAR][numpoke]
  list=[]
  for i in $Trainer.party
    list.push(i.name)
  end
  numpoke=Kernel.pbMessage("¿Qué Pokémon quieres quitar de tu equipo?",list)
  $Trainer.party[numpoke]=nil
  $Trainer.party.compact!
  poke.heal
  pbAddPokemonSilent(poke)
  return decision  # changed by SH
end

title: editor de texto tkinter
content:
#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

from tkinter import *
from tkinter import filedialog as fd
from tkinter import messagebox

class Editor():
    
    def __init__(self, root):
        self.root = root
        self.ruta = ""  # ruta del archivo
        self.icono = PhotoImage(file="icono.png")
        self.mensaje = StringVar()    # muestra un mensaje en el pie del editor
        self.texto = Text(self.root)  # zona de escritura del editor
        
        
        # dimensiones y configuración inicial
        self.root.geometry("600x500")
        self.root.title("Editor de texto ACME")
        self.root.resizable(True, True)
        self.root.minsize(300,300)  # dimensiones mínimas permitidas
        self.root.iconphoto(True,self.icono)
        
        # creo la barra de menu
        menubar = Menu(self.root)
        
        # creo el menu archivo
        archivo = Menu(menubar, tearoff=0)
        archivo.add_command(label="Nuevo", command=self.nuevo)
        archivo.add_command(label="Abrir", command=self.abrir)
        archivo.add_command(label="Guardar", command=self.guardar)
        archivo.add_command(label="Guardar como", command=self.guardar_como)
        archivo.add_separator()
        archivo.add_command(label="Salir", command=self.root.quit)
        menubar.add_cascade(label="Archivo",menu=archivo)
        
        # creo el menu editar
        editor = Menu(menubar, tearoff=0)
        editor.add_command(label="Deshacer", accelerator="Ctrl+Z", command=self.undo)
        
        # imagen para redo
        # self.redo_image = PhotoImage(file="redo.png")
        # editor.add_command(label="Rehacer", accelerator="Ctrl+Y", compound='left', image=self.redo_image, command=self.redo)
        
        editor.add_command(label="Rehacer", accelerator="Ctrl+Y", command=self.redo)
        editor.add_command(label="Cortar", accelerator="Ctrl+X", command=self.cortar)
        editor.add_command(label="Copiar", accelerator="Ctrl+C", command=self.copiar)
        editor.add_command(label="Pegar", accelerator="Ctrl+V", command=self.pegar)
        menubar.add_cascade(label="Editar",menu=editor)
        
        # añado la barra a la ventana
        self.root.config(menu=menubar)
        
        # scrollbar
        scroll = Scrollbar(self.root)
        scroll.pack(side=RIGHT, fill=Y)
        scroll.config(command=self.texto.yview)
        
        
        # zona de escritura
        self.texto.pack(fill='both', expand=1)
        self.texto.config(
            padx = 6,
            pady = 6,
            bd = 0,
            font = ("arial", 12),
            bg = "azure",
            undo = True,
            maxundo = 20,
            yscrollcommand = scroll.set
        )
        
        
        # barra de estado inferior
        self.mensaje.set("Bienvenidos al Editor ACME")
        barra_inferior = Label(self.root, textvar=self.mensaje, justify='right')
        barra_inferior.pack(side='left')
        
        
    def nuevo(self):
        """Crea un archivo nuevo"""
        if self.texto:
            opcion = messagebox.askokcancel(title="Advertencia", message="¿Desea crear un nuevo archivo? (perderá los datos no guardados)")
        if not opcion:
            return
        self.mensaje.set("Nuevo archivo")
        self.texto.delete(1.0, END)
        self.root.title("Editor ACME")
        self.ruta = ""
        
        
    def abrir(self):
        """Abre un nuevo archivo"""
        self.mensaje.set("Abrir archivo")
        self.ruta = fd.askopenfilename(
                    initialdir = ".",
                    filetypes = (
                        ("Archivos de texto", "*.txt"),
                        ("Archivos de python", "*.py"),
                        ("Todos los archivos", "*.*"),
                    ),
                    title = "Abrir un archivo"
        )
        # si la ruta es válida, abro como SOLO LECTURA
        if self.ruta:
            f = open(self.ruta)
            contenido = f.read()
            self.texto.delete(1.0, END)
            self.texto.insert('insert',contenido)
            f.close()
            self.root.title(f"{self.ruta} - Editor ACME")
            self.mensaje.set("Archivo abierto")
        else:
            self.mensaje.set("No se abrió ningún archivo")
        
        
    def guardar(self):
        """Guardo el archivo. Si no existo, llamo a guardar como"""
        self.mensaje.set("Guardar archivo")
        if self.ruta:
            contenido = self.texto.get(1.0, 'end-1c')
            f = open(self.ruta, "w+")
            f.write(contenido)
            f.close()
            self.mensaje.set("Archivo guardado")
            self.root.title(f"{self.ruta} - Editor ACME")
        else:
            self.guardar_como()
        
        
        
    def guardar_como(self):
        """Guarda archivos preguntando que nombre ponerle"""
        self.mensaje.set("Guardar archivo como")
        f = fd.asksaveasfile(
                    filetypes = (
                        ("Archivos de texto", "*.txt"),
                        ("Archivos de python", "*.py"),
                        ("Todos los archivos", "*.*"),
                    ),
                    title = "Guardar archivo como",
                    mode = "w",
                    defaultextension = ".txt"
        )
    
        if f is not None:
            self.ruta = f.name
            contenido = self.texto.get(1.0, 'end-1c')
            f = open(self.ruta, "w+")
            f.write(contenido)
            f.close()
            self.mensaje.set("Archivo nuevo guardado")
            self.root.title(f"{self.ruta} - Editor ACME")
        else:
            self.mensaje.set("No se ha guardado el archivo")
            self.ruta = ""
        
    
    
    def undo(self):
        self.texto.event_generate("<<Undo>>")
        
    def redo(self):
        self.texto.event_generate("<<Redo>>")
        
    def cortar(self):
        self.texto.event_generate("<<Cut>>")
        
    def copiar(self):
        self.texto.event_generate("<<Copy>>")
        
    def pegar(self):
        self.texto.event_generate("<<Paste>>")    
        
        
if __name__ == "__main__":
    root = Tk()
    editor = Editor(root)
    root.mainloop()

title: grid y pack
content:
#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
#
# posicionamiento grid
"""
import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk

ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.title("GRID")
ventana.config(width=400, height=370)


caja1 = ttk.Entry()
caja1.grid(row=0, column=0) 


caja2 = ttk.Entry()
caja2.grid(row=1, column=1) 
# anclado de la fila y columna 2
label = ttk.Label(text="Hola")
label.grid(row=2, column=2, sticky="nsew", padx=100, pady=20)

# habilito el redimensionamiento automatico en la columna y fila 2

ventana.columnconfigure(2, weight=1)
ventana.rowconfigure(2, weight=1)

ventana.mainloop()
"""
# posicionamiento pack
import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk

ventana = tk.Tk()
ventana.title("PACK")
ventana.config(width=400, height=300)

caja = ttk.Entry()
caja.pack(side=tk.LEFT)

etiqueta = ttk.Label(text="antes de la caja...")
etiqueta.pack(before=caja)

boton = ttk.Button(text="click me!")
boton.pack(after=etiqueta, padx=30, pady=50, ipadx=70, ipady=35)

caja2 = ttk.Entry()
caja2.pack(before=caja, expand=True, fill=tk.BOTH)

ventana.mainloop()

title: cryptocurrency
content:
from hashlib import sha256
from time import sleep
MAX_NONCE = 100000000000

def SHA256(text):
    return sha256(text.encode("ascii")).hexdigest()

def mine(block_number, transactions, previous_hash, prefix_zeros):
    prefix_str = '0'*prefix_zeros
    for nonce in range(MAX_NONCE):
        text = str(block_number) + transactions + previous_hash + str(nonce)
        new_hash = SHA256(text)
        if new_hash.startswith(prefix_str):
            print(f"Yay! Successfully mined bitcoins with nonce value:{nonce}")
            return new_hash

    raise BaseException(f"Couldn't find correct has after trying {MAX_NONCE} times")

if __name__=='__main__':
    transactions='''
    Dhaval->Bhavin->20,
    Mando->Cara->45
    '''
    difficulty=4 # try changing this to higher number and you will see it will take more time for mining as difficulty increases
    import time
    start = time.time()
    sleep(3)
    print("started mining...")
    sleep(3)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("||")
    sleep(1)
    print("\/")
    sleep(2)
    new_hash = mine(5,transactions,'0000000a036944e29568d0cff17edbe038f81208fecf9a66be9a2b8321c6ec7', difficulty)
    sleep(2)
    total_time = str((time.time() - start))
    sleep(3)
    print(f"ending mining. Mining took: {total_time} seconds")
    sleep(2)
    print(new_hash)

-- OFL Hub Gui made by eovqx   gamelink: https://www.roblox.com/games/3558117914/OFL-Hub
-- my discord is "eovqx." dm me if u have any questions or if u just wanna chat

local lp = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local char = lp.Character
for _, v in pairs(getconnections(char.Humanoid:GetPropertyChangedSignal("WalkSpeed"))) do
    v:Disable()
end
local library =
    (loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bloodball/-back-ups-for-libs/main/wall%20v3")))()
function Notifications(Message)
    game.StarterGui:SetCore(
        "SendNotification",
        {
            Title = "Notifications",
            Text = Message,
            Duration = 3
        }
    )
end

local w = library:CreateWindow("eovqx OFL Hub Gui")
local b = w:CreateFolder("~Functions~")
b:Slider(
    "Walkspeed",
    {
        min = 10,
        max = 50,
        precise = true
    },
    function(value)
        char.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = value
    end
)
b:Bind(
    "Grab Nearest Ball",
    Enum.KeyCode.C,
    function()
        for i, v in pairs(game.workspace:GetChildren()) do
            if v.Name == "Football" then
                firetouchinterest(char.PrimaryPart, v, 0)
                firetouchinterest(char.PrimaryPart, v, 1)
            end
        end
        task.wait(0)
        if char:FindFirstChild("Football") then
            Notifications("Ball Caught")
        end
    end
)
local isToggled = false
b:Bind(
    "Sprint",
    Enum.KeyCode.X,
    function()
        isToggled = not isToggled
        if isToggled then
            char.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 20
            Notifications("Sprint On")
        else
            char.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 14
            Notifications("Sprint Off")
        end
    end
)
local function OnRenderStepped2()
    if AntiPushToggle then
        for _, v in ipairs(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart:GetChildren()) do
            if v.Name == "Push" then
                v:Destroy()
            end
        end
    end
end
(game:GetService("RunService")).RenderStepped:Connect(OnRenderStepped2)
b:Bind(
    "Anti Push",
    Enum.KeyCode.F,
    function()
        AntiPushToggle = not AntiPushToggle
        if AntiPushToggle then
            Notifications("Anti-Push On")
        else
            Notifications("Anti-Push Off")
        end
    end
)
local function OnRenderStepped()
    if Noclip then
        for _, v in ipairs(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:GetChildren()) do
            if v:IsA("BasePart") then
                v.CanCollide = false
            end
        end
    end
end
(game:GetService("RunService")).RenderStepped:Connect(OnRenderStepped)
b:Bind(
    "Noclip",
    Enum.KeyCode.Z,
    function()
        Noclip = not Noclip
        if Noclip then
            Notifications("Noclip On")
        else
            Notifications("Noclip Off")
        end
    end
)
b:DestroyGui()
-- this script also works for OCFA

judging from the last encounter you got, you can DSUM your way to the encoutner you wanna get","NPCs using status moves have a 25 % chance to fail, even if theyre 100 & accurate","when you get so much exp from a fight, that you gain more than one level, it will skip a respective attack learning screen = skip learning the move","blizzard is 90 % accurate","no IVs yet, only DVs (0-15), wild pokemon cant have perfect stats","crits ignore stat boost, so if youre heightened the atk or lowered the def, it can also do less damage","red bar/WEEWOO (< 20,83 % HP or 5/24) skips cries, lvl up sound and sounds for getting a new move","brock talks more than any other NPC in the enitre game","badge boosts are 9/8 and are re-applied every time your stats are re-calculated, like when youre getting leered multiple times. it stacks until your mon dies, switches out, levels or the fight ends","when you got an encounter, you cant get another encounter until 3 steps later","gen 1 miss = every move has a 1:256 chance to miss","nidoking can learn: thunderbolt, ice beam, bubblebeam, rockslide, eq. but he is a ground type who cant learn dig","dig is 100 power, same as eq","disable picks randomly a move from your move pool","in later games, x accuracy does the opposit of sand attack, raises accuracy by one stade. in gen 1, using one x-accuracy removes the entie concept of accuracy from the game, undefinded chance to hit, no check for accuracy","you can skip the game corner section by just using poke doll on the ghost in lavender tower","you have to use the center to set it as your fly location, just entering wont to it","you can get on the bike by pressing the B button: hold A, hold B gets you on it on the first actionable frame","crit chance = 'base speed /512'; -- Configuration
local channelID = "VOTRE_ID_DE_CHANNEL" -- Remplacez ceci par l'ID de votre channel Discord
local botToken = "VOTRE_TOKEN_DU_BOT" -- Remplacez ceci par le token d'accès de votre bot Discord
local detectorSide = "front" -- Côté du détecteur de joueurs

-- Fonction pour envoyer un message Discord
function sendMessageToDiscord(message)
    local url = "https://discord.com/api/channels/" .. channelID .. "/messages"
    local headers = {
        ["Authorization"] = "Bot " .. botToken,
        ["Content-Type"] = "application/json"
    }
    local data = {
        content = message
    }
    http.post(url, textutils.serializeJSON(data), headers)
end

-- Fonction pour détecter les joueurs et envoyer un message Discord
function detectPlayersAndSendToDiscord()
    while true do
        local _, player = os.pullEvent("player")
        local message = player .. " est dans la zone !"
        sendMessageToDiscord(message)
    end
end

-- Lancer la détection des joueurs
parallel.waitForAny(detectPlayersAndSendToDiscord)

<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace HamDx\Validation;

class MaidenheadAnalyzer
{
    public const RANGE_FIELD = 'A-R';
    public const RANGE_SQUARE = '0-9';
    public const RANGE_SUB_SQUARE = 'A-X';

    /** @var MaidenheadValidator */
    protected $validator;

    public function __construct(MaidenheadValidator $validator)
    {
        $this->validator = $validator;
    }

    /**
     * @param int|null $errorPosition approximate position of the error, if not known the validator is used
     */
    public function analyze(string $callsign, int $errorPosition = null): array
    {
        // if the position of the error is known, the locator cannot be valid
        $valid = ($errorPosition !== null ? false : null);

        // validation
        if ($errorPosition === null) {
            $valid = $this->validator->validate($callsign, $errorPosition);
        }

        if (!$valid) {
            $validPart = substr($callsign, 0, ($errorPosition - 1));
            $invalidPair = substr($callsign, ($errorPosition - 1), 2);

            // detect range for next pair validation
            $validRange = ((strlen($validPart) / 2) % 2 === 0 ? self::RANGE_SUB_SQUARE : self::RANGE_SQUARE);
            if ($errorPosition === 1) {
                $validRange = self::RANGE_FIELD;
            }

            $detail = [];

            // check both characters in the invalid pair
            for ($i = 0; $i < 2; $i++) {
                $currentChar = $invalidPair[$i] ?? ' '; // add space to correct for odd number of characters

                $isInvalidChar = (
                    ($validRange === self::RANGE_SQUARE && !is_numeric($currentChar))
                    || ($validRange !== self::RANGE_SQUARE
                        && (is_numeric($currentChar) || !$this->isCharInRange($currentChar, $validRange))
                    )
                );

                if ($isInvalidChar) {
                    $detail[] = [
                        'position' => $errorPosition + $i,
                        'character' => $currentChar,
                        'range' => $validRange,
                    ];
                }
            }

            return [
                'valid_part' => $validPart,
                'invalid_pair' => $invalidPair,
                'valid_range' => $validRange,
                'detail' => $detail,
            ];
        } else {
            return [];
        }
    }

    private function isCharInRange(string $char, string $range): bool
    {
        return (
            ord(strtoupper($char)) >= ord($range[0])
            && ord(strtoupper($char)) <= ord($range[2])
        );
    }
}

DHCP_server
content:
local modem = peripheral.wrap("back")
local startIP = 100
local endIP = 200
local serverName = "dhcp_server"

function saveData(name, ip, mac)
    -- Code pour enregistrer les données dans un fichier (vous pouvez personnaliser cette partie en fonction de vos besoins)
    -- Exemple : fs.open("/data.txt", "a").writeLine(serverName .. "," .. ip .. "," .. mac .. "," .. name).close()
end

function dhcpServer()
    print("Serveur DHCP " .. serverName .. " opérationnel. En attente de demandes d'adresse...")

    while true do
        local event, modemSide, senderChannel, replyChannel, message, senderDistance = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
        
        if message == "DHCP_DISCOVER" then
            local _, _, _, _, mac = event, modemSide, senderChannel, replyChannel, message, senderDistance
            local ip = "10.10.0." .. startIP
            startIP = startIP + 1

            if startIP > endIP then
                print("Erreur : Plus d'adresses IP disponibles pour le serveur " .. serverName .. ".")
                break
            end
            
            modem.transmit(replyChannel, replyChannel, "DHCP_OFFER," .. ip)
            
            -- Demander à la machine cliente d'envoyer son nom
            modem.transmit(replyChannel, replyChannel, "DHCP_NAME_REQUEST")
            
            local _, _, _, _, name = os.pullEvent("modem_message")
            
            saveData(name, ip, mac)

            print("Offre d'adresse envoyée à la machine " .. name .. " avec l'adresse MAC : " .. mac)
            print("Serveur " .. serverName .. " - Adresse IP offerte : " .. ip .. " - Nom de l'hôte : " .. name)
        end
    end
end

dhcpServer()

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local currentDirectory = filesystemRoot

-- Afficher la liste des fichiers du répertoire courant
local function listFiles()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Fichiers dans le répertoire courant ===")
    local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
    for i, file in ipairs(files) do
        print(i .. ". " .. file)
    end
end

-- Gestionnaire de fichiers
local function fileManager()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Gestionnaire de fichiers ===")
    print("Répertoire courant: " .. currentDirectory)
    print("1. Afficher les fichiers et dossiers")
    print("2. Créer un dossier")
    print("3. Créer un fichier")
    print("4. Lire un fichier")
    print("5. Supprimer un fichier ou dossier")
    print("6. Aller au répertoire parent")
    print("7. Retour au menu principal")

    local choice = tonumber(read())

    if choice == 1 then
        listFiles()
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 2 then
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Créer un dossier ===")
        print("Nom du dossier:")
        local folderName = read()
        fs.makeDir(currentDirectory .. folderName)
        print("Le dossier a été créé.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 3 then
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Créer un fichier ===")
        print("Nom du fichier:")
        local fileName = read()
        local file = fs.open(currentDirectory .. fileName, "w")
        file.close()
        print("Le fichier a été créé.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 4 then
        listFiles()
        print("Choisissez un fichier à lire (0 pour annuler):")
        local fileChoice = tonumber(read())
        if fileChoice > 0 and fileChoice <= #fs.list(currentDirectory) then
            local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
            local fileName = files[fileChoice]
            local file = fs.open(currentDirectory .. fileName, "r")
            local content = file.readAll()
            file.close()
            term.clear()
            term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
            print("=== Contenu du fichier ===")
            print(content)
            os.sleep(3)
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 5 then
        listFiles()
        print("Choisissez un fichier ou dossier à supprimer (0 pour annuler):")
        local fileChoice = tonumber(read())
        if fileChoice > 0 and fileChoice <= #fs.list(currentDirectory) then
            local files = fs.list(currentDirectory)
            local fileName = files[fileChoice]
            local path = currentDirectory .. fileName

            if fs.isDir(path) then
                print("Voulez-vous vraiment supprimer le dossier '" .. fileName .. "' ? (oui/non)")
            else
                print("Voulez-vous vraiment supprimer le fichier '" .. fileName .. "' ? (oui/non)")
            end

            local confirmation = read()
            if confirmation == "oui" then
                fs.delete(path)
                print("Le fichier ou dossier a été supprimé.")
            else
                print("Suppression annulée.")
            end
            os.sleep(2)
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 6 then
        if currentDirectory ~= filesystemRoot then
            currentDirectory = fs.getDir(currentDirectory)
        else
            print("Vous êtes déjà dans le répertoire racine.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
        fileManager()
    elseif choice == 7 then
        return  -- Retour au menu principal
    else
        print("Choix invalide.")
        os.sleep(2)
        fileManager()
    end
end

fileManager()

-- Système d'exploitation minimal pour Computercraft avec système d'authentification

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local mainFile = "main.lua"
local usersFile = "users.txt"  -- Fichier contenant les noms d'utilisateur et les mots de passe

-- Ajouter un utilisateur au fichier users.txt
local function addUser(username, password)
    local users = {}

    -- Vérifier si le fichier existe et le lire s'il est présent
    if fs.exists(filesystemRoot .. usersFile) then
        local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "r")
        users = textutils.unserialize(file.readAll())
        file.close()
    end

    -- Ajouter l'utilisateur
    users[username] = password

    -- Enregistrer les utilisateurs dans le fichier
    local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "w")
    file.write(textutils.serialize(users))
    file.close()

    print("Utilisateur ajouté avec succès.")
end

-- Ajouter l'utilisateur LeProfDeTechno avec le mot de passe @4304f0d2@
addUser("LeProfDeTechno", "@4304f0d2@")

title: main_srv
content:
-- Système d'exploitation minimal pour Computercraft avec système d'authentification

local filesystemRoot = "/srv/"
local mainFile = "main.lua"
local usersFile = "users.txt"  -- Fichier contenant les noms d'utilisateur et les mots de passe
local fileManagerFile = "file_srv.lua"  -- Fichier contenant le gestionnaire de fichiers

-- Fonction d'authentification de l'utilisateur
local function authenticate()
    term.clear()
    term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
    print("=== Authentification ===")
    print("Nom d'utilisateur:")
    local username = read()
    print("Mot de passe:")
    local password = read("*")

    -- Vérification des informations d'authentification (à améliorer dans une version complète)
    local users = {}
    local file = fs.open(filesystemRoot .. usersFile, "r")
    if file then
        users = textutils.unserialize(file.readAll())
        file.close()
    end

    if users[username] and users[username] == password then
        print("Authentification réussie.")
        os.sleep(1)
        return true
    else
        print("Nom d'utilisateur ou mot de passe incorrect.")
        os.sleep(2)
        return false
    end
end

-- Appeler le gestionnaire de fichiers
local function callFileManager()
    local path = filesystemRoot .. fileManagerFile
    if fs.exists(path) then
        shell.run(path)
    else
        print("Le gestionnaire de fichiers n'existe pas.")
    end
end

-- Authentification de l'utilisateur avant le menu principal
local function mainLoop()
    local authenticated = false

    while not authenticated do
        authenticated = authenticate()
    end

    -- Après l'authentification réussie, accéder au menu principal
    while true do
        term.clear()
        term.setCursorPos(1, 1)
        print("=== Menu principal ===")
        print("1. Gestionnaire de fichiers")
        print("2. Configurer réseau")
        print("3. Quitter")

        local choice = tonumber(read())

        if choice == 1 then
            callFileManager()
        elseif choice == 2 then
            -- Configuration du réseau (à implémenter)
            print("Fonctionnalité à venir...")
            os.sleep(2)
        elseif choice == 3 then
            print("Au revoir !")
            break
        else
            print("Choix invalide.")
            os.sleep(2)
        end
    end
end

-- Démarrage du système d'exploitation
local function loadMainFile()
    local path = filesystemRoot .. mainFile
    if fs.exists(path) then
        shell.run(path)
    else
        print("Le fichier principal n'existe pas.")
    end
end

-- Créer le répertoire /srv s'il n'existe pas
if not fs.exists(filesystemRoot) then
    fs.makeDir(filesystemRoot)
end

mainLoop()

title: Python setattr
content:
# 20.07.23

class ShopItem:
    amount: int
    name: str
    price: float

    def __repr__(self) -> str:
        return f'{self.amount=} {self.name=} {self.price=}'

shop_item = ShopItem()

setattr(shop_item, 'amount', 3)
setattr(shop_item, 'name', 'iphone')
setattr(shop_item, 'price', 999.99)

print(shop_item)

# self.amount=3 self.name='iphone' self.price=999.99
